> library(smriti)
> 
> # Test 1: Basic functionality and NA removal
> cat("Running Test 1: Basic functionality and NA removal...\n")
Running Test 1: Basic functionality and NA removal...
> df <- data.frame(A = c(1, 2, NA, 4), B = c(NA, 2, 3, 4))
> result <- smriti::smriti_impute(df, time_cols = c("A", "B"), robust = FALSE)
Warning messages:
1: In smriti::smriti_impute(df, time_cols = c("A", "B"), robust = FALSE) :
  initial_imputation is NULL. Falling back to simple column-mean imputation. For better results, consider passing an initial imputation from 'missRanger' or 'mice'.
2: In smriti::smriti_impute(df, time_cols = c("A", "B"), robust = FALSE) :
  Covariance projection did not reach tolerance. Final Dist: 4.6100e-01 (Tol: 1.0000e-06).
> 
> # Assertion: All NAs must be gone
> if (any(is.na(result))) {
+   stop("Test 1 Failed: Imputed dataset still contains NAs.")
+ }
> cat("Test 1 Passed.\n")
Test 1 Passed.
> 
> # Test 2: Structural Integrity (Observed values untouched)
> cat("Running Test 2: Observed value preservation...\n")
Running Test 2: Observed value preservation...
> # If observed values changed, crash the test
> if (result$A[1] != 1) {
+   stop(sprintf("Test 2 Failed: Observed value A[1] changed from 1 to %f", result$A[1]))
+ }
> if (result$B[2] != 2) {
+   stop(sprintf("Test 2 Failed: Observed value B[2] changed from 2 to %f", result$B[2]))
+ }
> cat("Test 2 Passed.\n")
Test 2 Passed.
> 
> # Test 3: Custom Target implementation
> cat("Running Test 3: Custom Target...\n")
Running Test 3: Custom Target...
> target <- matrix(c(1, 0.5, 0.5, 1), 2, 2)
> result_custom <- smriti::smriti_impute(df, time_cols = c("A", "B"), custom_target = target)
Warning messages:
1: In smriti::smriti_impute(df, time_cols = c("A", "B"), custom_target = target) :
  initial_imputation is NULL. Falling back to simple column-mean imputation. For better results, consider passing an initial imputation from 'missRanger' or 'mice'.
2: In smriti::smriti_impute(df, time_cols = c("A", "B"), custom_target = target) :
  Covariance projection did not reach tolerance. Final Dist: 6.2252e-01 (Tol: 1.0000e-06).
> if (any(is.na(result_custom))) {
+   stop("Test 3 Failed: Custom target imputation contains NAs.")
+ }
> cat("Test 3 Passed.\n")
Test 3 Passed.
> 
> cat("\nAll critical unit tests passed successfully.\n")

All critical unit tests passed successfully.
